    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Error Workflow Configuration\n\n1. **Slack Notifications** (Optional)\n   - Add Slack API credentials\n   - Set channel name (default: #errors)\n   - Disable node if not using Slack\n\n2. **Email Notifications** (Optional)\n   - Add SMTP credentials\n   - Set recipient email address\n   - Disable node if not using email\n\n3. **Usage**\n   - This workflow is triggered automatically by errors in other workflows\n   - No manual trigger needed\n   - Other workflows reference this by ID in their error handlers\n\n4. **Customization**\n   - Add logging to external services (Sentry, LogRocket, etc.)\n   - Add retry logic\n   - Add PagerDuty integration for critical errors",
